{"type":"message","id":"6ea63534","parentId":"c6981890","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:33:57.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only active session is the current cron session itself (the session that just ran the check). This is not a \"活跃对话\" with a user - it's the cron job checking itself. There are no user messages in the last 5 minutes. I should execute the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务.","thinkingSignature":"8f5373897508bbb1c837ffa15427f0bef5122395a28a015cd251676015395528"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nowuzqrzqc3p_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:","limit":2}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":809,"output":117,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44907,"cost":{"input":0.0002427,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017025299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774640034098}}
